object, rotation handles, and rotation feedback 
(three rings) rotate around the center of rotation 
(see <XREF IDREF="87889" TYPE="GRAPHIC">Figure&nbsp;15-7</XREF>). All user input is interpreted to 
follow the virtual trackball.</PARAGRAPH>
</CELL>
</ROW>
<ROW><CELL LEFT="0" WIDTH="49"><PARAGRAPH>Release<INDEXTARGET ID="ch15.3Dmanip45"><!-- POSTPROCESSDATA: ch15.3Dmanip45|release phase:rotation --></PARAGRAPH>
